	   <tr><td colspan=2>Best place to get these is the siren enticers in sirens grotto.&nbsp;&nbsp;Just take care not to aggro the nearby elemental.  The enticer only hits for around 60 to 70, but is an enchanter so you get charmed and what not.  Buff up magic resist.  You should get one flawless diamond about every 2 hours of hunting plus other gems like the pristine emerald.  You can either hold out for the flawless diamond or just accumulate all the gems and buy your left over flawless in the bazaar.<br><br>siren is gimp.  Hardest part is getting to her camp.  Sea horses dont follow you out of the water though so you just have to make it there.  Easiest way is to succor accross the zone and then swim down the tube.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
