	   <tr><td colspan=2>The Flawless Diamond drops in Siren's Grotto a zone full of unmezzable mobs with 15k+ hp that hit for up to 200 damage and nearly always pull in mulitples. We have 1 in the guild. Corroded BP dropped for us also on a Kael raid. We were killing the extremely high level giants by the Temple of Rallos Zek. Siren's Grotto the diamond dropped right by the zone in. I think the basic tables are thus...<br>---------------------<br>XXX-A Zone Drops this gem off level 50-55 mobs<br>XXX-B Zone Drops this gem off level 55-60 mobs<br>---------------------<br>Risk/Reward...Siren's Grotto and Dragon Necropolis are worth incredibly rediculous amounts of exp...thus the parts for the armor are going to drop there. Be warned, the only way to get a group through Siren's alive is with the group Abscond/Succor spells. Fighting is futile in that zone for one group, you want 3-4 to make a dent, and even then each group would be holding a mob a piece...very tough zone. DN has these fun spawn traps...step on the wrong spot and OOPS! 6 mobs spawn on your part 55 plus beating the snot out of the one that stepped on trap...<br><br>Have fun...but hey! To be very honest I can't wait to go over to these zones, and I'm 60, just a matter of when our "deathgroup" starts out that way again =)<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
